data.description: Fully updated 3BR/2BA manufactured home in excellent condition with nice outbuildings, large decks, gorgeous mountain views and a lovely private pond. Improvements include replacement windows, new carpet, knockdown dry wall, wood siding and stone permanent foundation. Situated on two quiet acres, home offers peaceful country living with convenience to Greeneville and Interstate 81. Don't miss this great opportunity!
